<OUTPUT_TEXT>
Subject: Update on Your Recent Inquiry and Claim Status

Dear [Customer Name],

Thank you for reaching out to us regarding your recent inquiry and claim. We appreciate your patience as we conducted a thorough investigation.

We are pleased to inform you that the review of your claim has been completed. Based on our findings, [briefly state the outcome, e.g., "your claim has been approved and the necessary adjustments will be made to your account," or "we were unable to approve your claim at this time due to..."]. 

If any adjustments are planned, they will be reflected in your account within [timeframe, e.g., "the next 3-5 business days"]. Should you have any questions or require further clarification, please do not hesitate to contact us at [contact information].

Thank you for choosing [Company Name]. We value your business and are here to assist you with any further needs.

Best regards,

[Your Name]  
Senior Customer Service Representative  
[Company Name]  
[Contact Information]
</OUTPUT_TEXT>
